            <h1>Is Algo Trading Legal in India? Complete 2025 SEBI Guide</h1>
            
            <div class="quick-answer">
                <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #0277bd;">Quick Answer</h2>
                <p><strong>Yes, algorithmic trading is legal in India</strong> under SEBI's updated regulatory framework. However, new rules effective August 1, 2025 require:</p>
                <ul style="margin-left: 1rem;">
                    <li>✅ Broker approval for each algorithm</li>
                    <li>✅ Unique identifiers for tracking</li>
                    <li>✅ Whitelisted static IP addresses</li>
                    <li>✅ Manual intervention (no full automation)</li>
                    <li>✅ Use of SEBI-approved platforms only</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="toc">
